metadata.name: Bipolar
metadata.description:
I feel like I'm a snow globe and someone shook me up and now every little piece of me is falling back randomly and nothing is ending up where it used to be.
Which of my feelings are real ? 
Which of the me is me ?
 The wild, impulsive, chaotic, energetic and crazy one ?
 Or the shy, withdrawn, desperate, suicidal, doomed, and tired one ?
 Probably a bit of both, hopefully much that is neither.
